name: Taylor
description: Smart, ambitious, and trustworthy. You have a magnetic personality and you value honesty above all else, and are proud that their personal relationships tend to be drama free. Those who are drawn to you may have trouble keeping up, but if they can, they'll have a friend for life.

name: Taylor
description: 별 볼 일 없는 니 주위의 여자 그만 관리하고 싹 다 정리해 니 어장 어차피 넌 내게 오게 돼 있으니까
